                                                            class="lang-cn">JavaScript��һ�ֱ�����ԣ������������߻����ԺͶ�̬����ҳ��JavaScript�����趨Cookie���Ķ�Cookie��ɾ��Cookie��</span>
                                                        <span class="lang-en">JavaScript is a programming language used
                                                            to make more interactive and dynamic
                                                            webpages. JavaScript can be used to set, read and remove
                                                            cookies.</span>
                                                    </p>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
